<h2>English Language Proficiency Exam</h2>

<p>All UW students must write an English Language Proficiency Test during Orientation week, and must pass it before being allowed to enrol in certain senior courses. For more information see the University of Waterloo's <a href="http://elpp.uwaterloo.ca" target="_blank" style="color:blue;">English Language Proficiency Program website</a>.</p>

